This paper discusses privacy-preserving classification over encrypted data, which falls under the category of cryptography (cs.CR). The paper also deals with data mining and classification, which are topics in databases (cs.DB) and machine learning (cs.LG). The use of cloud computing is also mentioned, which could fall under the category of computer systems and networking (cs.CY) or distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
